videos.headline: NC State gets on board with 3-yard TD run
videos.description: NC State's Reggie Gallaspy squeezes into the end zone for a 3-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: BC stops NC State in red zone with interception
videos.description: Boston College's Zach Allen makes the Eagles' 9th interception of the season to halt an NC State drive.

videos.headline: Gallaspy gets second TD of day with 1-yard run
videos.description: Reggie Gallaspy widens the gap for NC State with his second rushing touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: Finley finds Meyers for 4-yard TD
videos.description: Ryan Finley connects with Jakobi Meyers in the end zone for a 4-yard NC State touchdown.

videos.headline: BC answers with 21-yard TD run
videos.description: Ben Glines weaves through the NC State defense for the first touchdown of the game for the Eagles.

videos.headline: Glines hauls in 11-yard pass for 2nd TD catch
videos.description: Boston College's Ben Glines puts the Eagles within 12 points on a successful 11-yard pass from Anthony Brown.

videos.headline: BC scores TD on blocked punt
videos.description: Travis Levy runs into the end zone for a Boston College touchdown after NC State's punt is blocked.
